notas (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Secure AES-256-GCM encryption for all notes
  * Argon2id key derivation with configurable parameters
  * GTK4 + libadwaita modern UI with custom header bar
  * macOS-style traffic light window controls
  * Dark and light theme support
  * 14 font families with customizable sizes
  * Auto-lock with configurable timeout
  * Automatic clipboard clearing
  * Secure import/export functionality
  * Toggle for note title visibility

